WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:02.590
Hey, good morning family, how are y'all

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:04.710
doing today? Well, I have some things on

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:06.670
my heart that the Lord has shown me, and

00:00:06.680 --> 00:00:08.509
I'm excited about this. He started

00:00:08.519 --> 00:00:10.709
talking to me about the outpouring of

00:00:10.719 --> 00:00:16.310
His Spirit again—a major change coming, a

00:00:16.310 --> 00:00:16.320
major—I'm

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:18.670
going to say it's like the

00:00:18.680 --> 00:00:21.830
tipping of the waterfall again.

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:23.269
And the things that the Lord is talking

00:00:23.279 --> 00:00:29.790
to me about, I saw a door, a massive door,

00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:33.590
and it was a white door, a beautiful

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:37.150
painted white door, but on this door

00:00:37.160 --> 00:00:39.590
there was purple, there

00:00:39.590 --> 00:00:39.600
were

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:42.110
swirls of different—like the glory of

00:00:42.120 --> 00:00:44.510
what I want to call the Shekinah Glory. It

00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:47.350
looked like mist, and it was covering

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:49.630
this door, but it was beautiful.

00:00:49.640 --> 00:00:51.630
The colors, the pinks and stuff, the

00:00:51.640 --> 00:00:54.670
clouds are in front of it and behind. In

00:00:54.680 --> 00:00:58.549
the door frame behind the door was like

00:00:58.559 --> 00:01:00.389
a dimension.

00:01:00.399 --> 00:01:04.750
Okay, and in that dimension behind it was

00:01:04.760 --> 00:01:08.630
the glory, and I could see the light

00:01:08.640 --> 00:01:12.469
coming through the cracks of the door.

00:01:12.479 --> 00:01:14.950
It was shining through that door

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:18.030
on the cracks, and I could see like

00:01:18.040 --> 00:01:20.429
it was just trying to bust

00:01:20.429 --> 00:01:20.439
through—the

00:01:20.439 --> 00:01:22.190
glory of God was trying to bust through

00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:27.149
this door. And behind it was the

00:01:27.159 --> 00:01:29.950
same, which was amazing. I

00:01:29.960 --> 00:01:32.310
don't know how else to describe this.

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:34.590
Behind it was the same dimension as the

00:01:34.600 --> 00:01:36.870
front side, but

00:01:36.880 --> 00:01:38.950
it was like a door that was standing

00:01:38.960 --> 00:01:41.030
all alone, but it was a door that you

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:43.630
could open up to it. And I had

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:45.310
to say it like this, but this is a way I

00:01:45.320 --> 00:01:46.789
can try—I'm trying to paint a picture

00:01:46.799 --> 00:01:48.870
for y'all like The Lion, the Witch and the

00:01:48.880 --> 00:01:51.030
Wardrobe, how there was a

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:52.149
closet and they walked through the

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:54.469
closet and they could go through the

00:01:54.479 --> 00:01:58.109
other dimension into Narnia.

00:01:58.119 --> 00:02:00.270
So that's kind of like what I saw. It was a door that was like

00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:06.469
a passage, but on the other side

00:02:06.479 --> 00:02:08.550
of it, without opening the door, He was

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:10.430
walking through the dimension. It was

00:02:10.440 --> 00:02:13.190
still in the same dimension because on this

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:15.509
side I could see the pink and all the

00:02:15.519 --> 00:02:17.630
beautiful stuff again. But the Lord said

00:02:17.640 --> 00:02:22.070
to me, 'Everything is about to change, for

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:26.030
in this space of time you've hit

00:02:26.040 --> 00:02:29.229
this where we are.'Help me, Holy

00:02:29.239 --> 00:02:30.550
Spirit.

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:33.390
He said, 'This dispensation of time is

00:02:33.400 --> 00:02:36.229
coming to an end.'That's what He was

00:02:36.239 --> 00:02:39.550
saying to me and where we are in it.

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:44.630
And I saw Adam's lease coming up again.

00:02:44.640 --> 00:02:46.229
It was

00:02:46.239 --> 00:02:50.270
up, and we were going into another space

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:54.790
of time. And He said to me, during Rosh

00:02:54.790 --> 00:02:54.800
Hashanah

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:57.309
this week—this week is an amazing

00:02:57.319 --> 00:03:00.270
week because this is the beginning

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:02.990
on the second, which is in two days, the

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:05.630
beginning of Rosh

00:03:05.630 --> 00:03:05.640
Hashanah,

00:03:05.640 --> 00:03:09.149
which goes into the third and I

00:03:09.159 --> 00:03:11.390
believe the fourth, at whenever the

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:13.430
new moon and all that is. I

00:03:13.430 --> 00:03:13.440
believe—I'm

00:03:13.440 --> 00:03:14.990
not going to quote right

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:16.710
because I am not a Jewish

00:03:16.710 --> 00:03:16.720
scholar—but

00:03:16.720 --> 00:03:19.190
I'm just saying this is what I've seen.

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:22.309
So He said, 'This time frame is the

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:25.270
beginning of the new

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:27.789
creative miracles, that we have hit a

00:03:27.799 --> 00:03:31.670
time and space that we've hit a time

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:34.710
in

00:03:34.720 --> 00:03:38.070
history where Adam's lease

00:03:38.070 --> 00:03:38.080
is

00:03:38.080 --> 00:03:40.869
coming up, that we are getting ready for

00:03:40.879 --> 00:03:43.270
the great outpouring and we're going

00:03:43.270 --> 00:03:43.280
home.'We're

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:46.390
getting ready to go home. I

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:50.630
saw the glory behind this door and I saw

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:52.910
the door was going to open. And He said,

00:03:52.920 --> 00:03:56.350
'In a 24-hour period, everything will

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:58.869
change. Everything that you know,

00:03:58.879 --> 00:04:01.030
everything that you've ever known up

00:04:01.040 --> 00:04:04.910
until this point in human history,

00:04:04.920 --> 00:04:06.949
everything will change like a light switch.'He said, 'Brandon, it's going to be like a light

00:04:06.959 --> 00:04:08.589
switch

00:04:08.599 --> 00:04:09.949
that

00:04:09.959 --> 00:04:12.470
flips on.'He said that time frame is

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:15.750
coming to an end, what we've seen, and He

00:04:15.760 --> 00:04:18.030
said, 'You're coming into a new time frame,

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:19.310
and you're going to cross and

00:04:19.320 --> 00:04:21.550
you're going to go through this

00:04:21.550 --> 00:04:21.560
door.'And

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:24.710
I saw the glory again upon the bride,

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:27.670
upon the body, in a way that is

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:33.710
huge. We think we've seen stuff

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:35.189
in the

00:04:35.189 --> 00:04:35.199
past—revivals,

00:04:35.199 --> 00:04:38.390
demonstrations, and

00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:41.390
manifestations of the glory, outpourings

00:04:41.400 --> 00:04:44.390
of when Azusa Street happened. You

00:04:44.400 --> 00:04:46.390
know, there was a prophetic word that was

00:04:46.400 --> 00:04:49.550
given over a hundred years ago

00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:51.830
now that said that there

00:04:51.840 --> 00:04:54.390
would be another revival like Azusa in

00:04:54.390 --> 00:04:54.400
a hundred

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:57.990
years that would be bigger

00:04:58.000 --> 00:05:00.510
than what happened at

00:05:00.510 --> 00:05:00.520
Azusa,

00:05:00.520 --> 00:05:03.590
and it's been going on 120-some years

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:05.830
now. But He said they didn't quite say

00:05:05.840 --> 00:05:07.070
it was going to be a hundred years, it would be

00:05:07.080 --> 00:05:11.150
in a hundred-year time frame. Well, we're in 120

00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:14.590
years. In two years, I believe, we're in

00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:16.710
that time frame of that prophetic word

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:20.230
that was given. So here we are at the

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:23.070
last of the last. I'm telling you all,

00:05:23.080 --> 00:05:25.990
Jesus is coming and the sun is

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:29.909
going down on this dispensation

00:05:29.919 --> 00:05:33.990
of grace. And I saw the devil petitioning

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:38.469
again for his seven-year tribulation. And

00:05:38.479 --> 00:05:41.469
I saw he had a—this time he had a black

00:05:41.479 --> 00:05:44.749
cloak on. It was a massive black cloak,

00:05:44.759 --> 00:05:46.670
and he was moving around very

00:05:46.680 --> 00:05:49.189
sneaky and just evil, the way he was

00:05:49.199 --> 00:05:51.749
moving. And he is lurching around,

00:05:51.759 --> 00:05:53.350
kind of like Snow White and the Seven

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:55.670
Dwarfs whenever that old witch was

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:57.629
there and she had that black cloak on.

00:05:57.639 --> 00:05:59.189
That's the way the devil

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:01.830
looked. But he was going and I saw him go

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:04.950
and he was talking to the Pope, which I

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:08.430
think is just a wow, but he was talking

00:06:08.440 --> 00:06:11.589
to the Pope, influencing the Vatican and

00:06:11.599 --> 00:06:15.270
the church in Rome. Because I

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:16.710
was like, 'What is that all about?'But I

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:18.950
saw the devil trying to go and influence

00:06:18.960 --> 00:06:21.790
and talk to the Pope in the Vatican and

00:06:21.800 --> 00:06:23.469
he was speaking to him. I don't

00:06:23.479 --> 00:06:24.990
even know if the Pope knew he was being

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:27.749
talked to, but he was. He was talking

00:06:27.759 --> 00:06:32.150
to the Pope, and

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:34.029
I saw the Pope and he

00:06:34.029 --> 00:06:34.039
had

00:06:34.039 --> 00:06:35.830
his white beanie

00:06:35.830 --> 00:06:35.840
on—his

00:06:35.840 --> 00:06:37.550
head thing—and he was looking

00:06:37.560 --> 00:06:39.230
down. But the devils were

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:41.510
standing behind him trying to influence

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:45.629
him, talking to him. And then I saw Italy

00:06:45.639 --> 00:06:49.350
and I saw cracks all in the soil

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:53.390
again with like lava and fire all over

00:06:53.400 --> 00:06:56.790
Italy again. I saw fire and it was like

00:06:56.800 --> 00:06:58.270
the earth was splitting,

00:06:58.280 --> 00:06:59.950
like from an earthquake, remember? And I

00:06:59.960 --> 00:07:02.430
warned you all about a volcano that the

00:07:02.440 --> 00:07:05.070
Lord told me to intercede in behalf of

00:07:05.080 --> 00:07:06.390
Italy, that there would be a lot of

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:08.589
people perish because of a tsunami

00:07:08.599 --> 00:07:11.629
in the water and because of volcanic

00:07:11.639 --> 00:07:13.510
activity. I told you this about a year

00:07:13.520 --> 00:07:16.029
ago. And when I was

00:07:16.039 --> 00:07:17.790
interceding, I saw the angels coming out

00:07:17.800 --> 00:07:19.589
of the sky and they were warning the

00:07:19.599 --> 00:07:21.309
people and waking them up. And there was

00:07:21.319 --> 00:07:23.950
a mist, like a

00:07:23.960 --> 00:07:25.869
canary in the coal mine. I told you all

00:07:25.879 --> 00:07:27.510
about the canary in the coal mine and it

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:29.510
was on the perch and it fell over

00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:31.469
dead, and there was a gas coming up

00:07:31.479 --> 00:07:33.950
out of the ground. And I saw

00:07:33.960 --> 00:07:37.070
like a mist, a fog over the land over

00:07:37.080 --> 00:07:39.270
this town in Italy, and it was on

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:41.350
the coastline. And the

00:07:41.360 --> 00:07:42.950
angels were warning the people and they

00:07:42.960 --> 00:07:44.710
were coming out, and I saw a portal open

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:46.830
up over Italy.

00:07:46.840 --> 00:07:49.589
If

00:07:49.599 --> 00:07:50.909
anybody who's followed this channel for

00:07:50.919 --> 00:07:53.830
a while remembers this, that I warned

00:07:53.840 --> 00:07:55.710
about this and we were interceding for

00:07:55.720 --> 00:07:58.670
Italy that this major earthquake would

00:07:58.680 --> 00:08:00.309
not take place and destroy a lot of

00:08:00.319 --> 00:08:03.029
people. I saw 300,000 people perish. And

00:08:03.039 --> 00:08:04.749
so

00:08:04.759 --> 00:08:08.869
I saw that again. I saw Italy

00:08:08.879 --> 00:08:11.790
splitting open, I saw fire coming up out

00:08:11.800 --> 00:08:14.070
of these cracks, and I thought it was

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:17.070
interesting. But I saw the Pope being

00:08:17.080 --> 00:08:19.790
influenced by a demon, by the devil,

00:08:19.800 --> 00:08:22.710
and he was talking to the devil. And

00:08:22.720 --> 00:08:27.710
so I saw in this time frame where we are

00:08:27.720 --> 00:08:31.550
in eternity and the Lord was telling

00:08:31.560 --> 00:08:34.430
me, He said, 'Brandon, we are at that

00:08:34.440 --> 00:08:37.269
sliver of

00:08:37.269 --> 00:08:37.279
time.'And

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:39.469
He said, 'And you know when the Bible

00:08:39.479 --> 00:08:42.630
says a day is a thousand years to the

00:08:42.640 --> 00:08:45.590
Lord, a thousand years is as a day,

00:08:45.600 --> 00:08:48.470
right?'So

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:54.150
I saw thousand, thousand,

00:08:54.160 --> 00:08:56.910
thousand, thousand—clear to the beginning of

00:08:56.920 --> 00:08:59.550
time the Lord showed me. And I'm

00:08:59.560 --> 00:09:01.110
telling you, I had an experience of the

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:03.590
Lord beyond anything I've been

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:07.110
able to ever tell you all, and I've told

00:09:07.120 --> 00:09:11.190
you all some amazing experiences. But

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:14.710
this experience that I had with the Lord

00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:17.350
was beyond anything I've ever

00:09:17.360 --> 00:09:20.790
seen before. It was

00:09:20.790 --> 00:09:20.800
like—to

00:09:20.800 --> 00:09:24.710
say it shook me—it

00:09:24.710 --> 00:09:24.720
was

00:09:24.720 --> 00:09:27.430
beyond saying it. My son and my

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:28.829
wife, they recorded it; they were here

00:09:28.839 --> 00:09:30.590
for it. And I'm not going to go into a

00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:31.990
lot of it because a lot of the word that

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:34.630
was given when I had this visitation

00:09:34.640 --> 00:09:37.069
about four or five days ago

00:09:37.079 --> 00:09:39.630
was so intense because

00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:42.870
He was speaking to me directly. And so a

00:09:42.880 --> 00:09:46.190
lot of it is not for the public.

00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:50.870
But in this, He showed me Adam's lease,

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:53.470
He showed me the door like I'm talking

00:09:53.480 --> 00:09:57.030
about, He showed me where we are in

00:09:57.040 --> 00:10:00.590
time again, and He took time

00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:02.310
on a thin

00:10:02.320 --> 00:10:06.670
line, a thread, and He spread it out by

00:10:06.680 --> 00:10:08.910
every thousand years. And He took me

00:10:08.920 --> 00:10:09.790
through

00:10:09.800 --> 00:10:12.870
time and it was way out there, but

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:16.150
I could see from the beginning

00:10:16.160 --> 00:10:17.910
whenever He spoke the world into

00:10:17.920 --> 00:10:20.590
existence. I saw Adam walking the earth, I

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:23.990
saw Noah and the flood. He took me to

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:26.389
each one and how they were milestones in

00:10:26.399 --> 00:10:30.230
history. And I saw each thing,

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:33.509
from the Roman Empire to the Ottoman

00:10:33.509 --> 00:10:33.519
Empire,

00:10:33.519 --> 00:10:36.230
He showed it to

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:39.069
me. But each thing was divided up into a

00:10:39.079 --> 00:10:41.230
thousand years, and then a thousand years

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:42.829
would divide up into a hundred years, and

00:10:42.839 --> 00:10:44.710
then it went down to ten years, to a

00:10:44.720 --> 00:10:47.389
decade. And He showed it out, it was on a

00:10:47.399 --> 00:10:49.910
timeline. And He took me

00:10:49.920 --> 00:10:52.629
through the timeline in space with Him,

00:10:52.639 --> 00:10:54.910
traveling to where we are right now,

00:10:54.920 --> 00:10:57.629
ladies and gentlemen. And I'm telling you,

00:10:57.639 --> 00:10:59.829
Jesus Christ is getting ready to

00:10:59.839 --> 00:11:03.350
come back, and He's coming back for not a

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:06.150
busted and disgusted church, He's coming

00:11:06.160 --> 00:11:08.670
back for a glorious church. He's coming

00:11:08.680 --> 00:11:11.389
back for a church that's on fire for Him.

00:11:11.399 --> 00:11:14.069
He is looking and yearning for His

00:11:14.079 --> 00:11:17.389
bride. And I'm telling you, it's time

00:11:17.399 --> 00:11:19.550
to get more serious than you've ever

00:11:19.560 --> 00:11:23.750
been before, for where we are in

00:11:23.750 --> 00:11:23.760
time—time

00:11:23.760 --> 00:11:27.910
is up, one last call. He said,

00:11:27.920 --> 00:11:30.430
'Remember, where we are right

00:11:30.430 --> 00:11:30.440
now,'He

00:11:30.440 --> 00:11:32.790
said, 'Brandon, I can

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:34.310
control

00:11:34.310 --> 00:11:34.320
time.'And

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:37.710
He showed me where

00:11:37.720 --> 00:11:40.389
Adam's lease and everything was up, but

00:11:40.399 --> 00:11:42.870
there was a sliver right here in between,

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:44.829
like a couple of seconds, like a

00:11:44.839 --> 00:11:46.190
couple minutes—you know what

00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:48.230
I'm saying—like it was a long

00:11:48.240 --> 00:11:51.629
enough time for Him to have His revival

00:11:51.639 --> 00:11:53.269
and be able to bring in a harvest of

00:11:53.279 --> 00:11:55.750
souls. He said, 'Because I have never been

00:11:55.760 --> 00:11:59.509
defeated nor will I ever be.'He said,

00:11:59.519 --> 00:12:02.990
'I will not allow

00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:06.910
you to run back and be afraid of what

00:12:06.920 --> 00:12:11.190
the devil is doing.'He said, 'You are to

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:13.829
put on your armor and be strong in the

00:12:13.839 --> 00:12:17.150
Lord in the power of His might.'It's time

00:12:17.160 --> 00:12:20.590
for us to be like the Davids. And He said,

00:12:20.600 --> 00:12:22.470
'There's a lot of people, Brandon, that are

00:12:22.470 --> 00:12:22.480
tired—the

00:12:22.480 --> 00:12:24.590
older generation, they're

00:12:24.600 --> 00:12:25.949
tired and they're ready to come

00:12:25.949 --> 00:12:25.959
home.'And

00:12:25.959 --> 00:12:28.590
He said, 'Allow that to happen.

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:29.910
If they're ready and they want to come

00:12:29.920 --> 00:12:32.949
home and they're satisfied,

00:12:32.959 --> 00:12:34.590
they can come

