thousand-year

00:23:28.520 --> 00:23:30.990
reign—He

00:23:31.000 --> 00:23:33.590
has such a plan for each and

00:23:33.600 --> 00:23:36.269
every single one of

00:23:36.279 --> 00:23:40.350
you. We will see creative

00:23:40.360 --> 00:23:44.310
miracles, we will see blind eyes open,

00:23:44.320 --> 00:23:48.510
we will see dead men walk again, we will

00:23:48.520 --> 00:23:51.230
see the things that we've

00:23:51.240 --> 00:23:53.669
always desired to see. And thought, 'Is it

00:23:53.669 --> 00:23:53.679
possible?'But

00:23:53.679 --> 00:23:56.430
I'm trying to tell you all

00:23:56.440 --> 00:23:59.310
things are possible to him that believes,

00:23:59.320 --> 00:24:02.630
and a great move of the Spirit of God is

00:24:02.640 --> 00:24:03.590
right on

00:24:03.600 --> 00:24:06.909
us. It's right here. And I want my wife—she's

00:24:06.909 --> 00:24:06.919
here—to

00:24:06.919 --> 00:24:09.149
read some of the testimonies, just to

00:24:09.159 --> 00:24:10.789
stir you up, just to get you excited

00:24:10.799 --> 00:24:13.390
about what's coming, about the miracles

00:24:13.400 --> 00:24:15.909
that took place at Azusa Street. We've

00:24:15.919 --> 00:24:17.070
been reading that book, and I told her,

00:24:17.080 --> 00:24:18.830
'Read it to me again, read it to me

00:24:18.830 --> 00:24:18.840
again.'Because

00:24:18.840 --> 00:24:20.669
faith cometh by hearing,

00:24:20.679 --> 00:24:22.269
and hearing by the Word of God. And this

00:24:22.279 --> 00:24:23.830
is not the Word of God, but this is

00:24:23.840 --> 00:24:25.950
something that God did in the past. And

00:24:25.960 --> 00:24:27.470
we read the Bible, but she reads

00:24:27.480 --> 00:24:29.110
these testimonies to me to show me,

00:24:29.120 --> 00:24:31.510
'Brandon, it's happened once and He's going

00:24:31.510 --> 00:24:31.520
to

00:24:31.520 --> 00:24:35.149
do it

00:24:35.149 --> 00:24:35.159
again.'There

00:24:35.159 --> 00:24:37.909
is a

00:24:37.919 --> 00:24:40.029
great outpouring, a great harvest of

00:24:40.039 --> 00:24:42.590
souls. I'm telling you, He's the Lord of

00:24:42.600 --> 00:24:45.350
the harvest. 'Hi everybody, I'm just

00:24:45.360 --> 00:24:49.110
reading a couple of miracles from

00:24:49.120 --> 00:24:52.190
the true stories of the miracles of

00:24:52.190 --> 00:24:52.200
Azusa

00:24:52.200 --> 00:24:55.870
Street... and there was—this is just

00:24:55.880 --> 00:24:57.350
one of the testimonies...

00:24:58.520 --> 00:25:01.350
these were just people

00:25:01.360 --> 00:25:04.110
that were there that God used

00:25:04.110 --> 00:25:04.120
to

00:25:04.120 --> 00:25:06.669
do healings

00:25:06.679 --> 00:25:09.350
and miracles.'And what we

00:25:09.360 --> 00:25:11.070
thought was cool, though, babe, was that

00:25:11.080 --> 00:25:12.870
a lot of these were young

00:25:12.880 --> 00:25:15.710
people. They were in the 18, 19, 12-year-olds—and

00:25:15.710 --> 00:25:15.720
21-year-olds—but

00:25:15.720 --> 00:25:20.110
no,

00:25:20.120 --> 00:25:21.350
a lot of these people were not old

00:25:21.360 --> 00:25:23.310
people. They were all young people.

00:25:23.320 --> 00:25:25.310
I'm talking about being young Davids,

00:25:25.320 --> 00:25:28.630
being on fire with no fear. And

00:25:28.640 --> 00:25:31.190
I look back at what He did at

00:25:31.190 --> 00:25:31.200
Azusa, and

00:25:31.200 --> 00:25:32.590
we're reading—she's reading about—she

00:25:32.590 --> 00:25:32.600
goes, 'Brandon,

00:25:32.600 --> 00:25:35.789
another 18-year-old, another

00:25:35.789 --> 00:25:35.799
21-year-old,

00:25:35.799 --> 00:25:38.590
another 12-year-old, another 15-year-old,

00:25:38.590 --> 00:25:38.600
16-year-old

00:25:38.600 --> 00:25:40.830
was doing

00:25:40.840 --> 00:25:43.750
creative miracles, praying for people

00:25:43.760 --> 00:25:46.310
that needed a limb or eyes or

00:25:46.310 --> 00:25:46.320
whatever.'It

00:25:46.320 --> 00:25:47.750
wasn't like, 'Well, this guy was a

00:25:47.760 --> 00:25:50.149
seasoned veteran that was

00:25:50.159 --> 00:25:52.070
a preacher

00:25:52.080 --> 00:25:55.669
for 45 years at the Assemblies of

00:25:55.669 --> 00:25:55.679
God.'No,

00:25:55.679 --> 00:25:57.470
these were people that were

00:25:57.480 --> 00:26:00.269
just hungry, weren't they? Yeah, and

00:26:00.279 --> 00:26:01.750
it's exciting to hear these stories

00:26:01.760 --> 00:26:03.190
because you always think, 'Well, I have to

00:26:03.190 --> 00:26:03.200
be—well,

00:26:03.200 --> 00:26:05.830
I'm not a pastor, I'm not an

00:26:05.840 --> 00:26:08.070
evangelist, I can't be used.'He was

00:26:08.080 --> 00:26:09.830
using average

00:26:09.840 --> 00:26:12.310
Joes. He's going to use

00:26:12.320 --> 00:26:15.750
you. You don't have to have a platform;

00:26:15.760 --> 00:26:17.510
you don't have to have something huge.

00:26:17.520 --> 00:26:19.029
Now, I'm sorry to cut you off, baby,

00:26:19.039 --> 00:26:20.549
but I'm just—I have to tell everybody,

00:26:20.559 --> 00:26:23.669
it's not somebody that has a huge church.

00:26:23.679 --> 00:26:25.190
He's going to use you, ladies and

00:26:25.200 --> 00:26:28.310
gentlemen. He's going to use you. You

00:26:28.320 --> 00:26:31.029
could just be a stay-at-home mom

00:26:31.039 --> 00:26:33.149
that's just doing homework on the

00:26:33.159 --> 00:26:34.990
weekdays with their kids

00:26:34.990 --> 00:26:35.000
and—'Hey

00:26:35.000 --> 00:26:36.870
man, I made dinner for my

00:26:36.870 --> 00:26:36.880
family'—but

00:26:36.880 --> 00:26:39.750
God's going to use you. He

00:26:39.750 --> 00:26:39.760
doesn't

00:26:39.760 --> 00:26:41.110
have to look—you don't have to

00:26:41.120 --> 00:26:43.630
have a huge church. Most of these people

00:26:43.630 --> 00:26:43.640
who

00:26:43.640 --> 00:26:46.389
have huge churches, they have egos anyway.

00:26:46.399 --> 00:26:48.310
Look at it:

00:26:48.320 --> 00:26:50.590
'Think of the movies The Elephant Man or

00:26:50.600 --> 00:26:52.350
Mask and you can picture the total

00:26:52.360 --> 00:26:56.230
disfigurement of this 25 to 30-year-old man

00:26:56.240 --> 00:26:58.590
who came to Azusa Street. He came there on

00:26:58.600 --> 00:27:00.590
his own, pathetically dragging his feet,

00:27:00.590 --> 00:27:00.600
sickening-looking,

00:27:00.600 --> 00:27:02.789
with one eye shooting

00:27:02.799 --> 00:27:04.990
up and the other looking down. His mind

00:27:05.000 --> 00:27:07.269
was perfectly fine, but he had been

00:27:07.279 --> 00:27:09.110
deformed and the condition grew worse

00:27:09.120 --> 00:27:11.710
and worse. He had been born deformed and

00:27:11.720 --> 00:27:13.590
the condition grew worse and worse. His

00:27:13.600 --> 00:27:16.909
mouth and jaw hung below his left breast.

00:27:16.919 --> 00:27:20.470
Mother Mangram

00:27:20.480 --> 00:27:22.350
made her way over'—this is one of the

00:27:22.360 --> 00:27:24.630
people that was there praying over

00:27:24.630 --> 00:27:24.640
people—'and

00:27:24.640 --> 00:27:26.909
made her way over to him, and

00:27:26.919 --> 00:27:29.230
he looked at her with his twisted eyes

00:27:29.240 --> 00:27:32.029
and uttered something. "What did you

00:27:32.029 --> 00:27:32.039
say?"asked

00:27:32.039 --> 00:27:34.870
Mother Mangram. He mumbled, "I came

00:27:34.880 --> 00:27:38.149
here to get healed."She said, "Oh, praise

00:27:38.159 --> 00:27:39.789
God, you're going to have a great

00:27:39.789 --> 00:27:39.799
testimony."He

00:27:39.799 --> 00:27:43.029
said, "Okay, I'm

00:27:43.029 --> 00:27:43.039
ready."I

00:27:43.039 --> 00:27:46.070
love the fact that he came to

00:27:46.070 --> 00:27:46.080
Azusa

00:27:46.080 --> 00:27:49.710
ready. She slapped hands on him and

00:27:49.720 --> 00:27:52.710
held him there as his body danced under

00:27:52.720 --> 00:27:55.470
her touch. His face started contorting

00:27:55.480 --> 00:27:57.710
and coming back together. His jaw

00:27:57.720 --> 00:28:00.389
withdrew into place, his eyes

00:28:00.399 --> 00:28:02.830
rotated in their sockets, and his back,

00:28:02.840 --> 00:28:05.750
legs, and hands untwisted. I asked how

00:28:05.760 --> 00:28:08.350
long it took. She said a very attractive

00:28:08.360 --> 00:28:10.470
man stood in front of her in about five

00:28:10.480 --> 00:28:13.830
minutes. Praise God! Over two decades of

00:28:13.840 --> 00:28:16.669
deformity were made perfect in five

00:28:16.679 --> 00:28:19.630
minutes. I never found out his name. He

00:28:19.640 --> 00:28:21.830
became a minister after God blessed him

00:28:21.840 --> 00:28:24.029
with his healing. I believe this miracle

00:28:24.039 --> 00:28:25.750
alone could start an

00:28:25.760 --> 00:28:28.630
awakening.'It

00:28:28.640 --> 00:28:30.590
just takes one. I'm telling you all,

00:28:30.590 --> 00:28:30.600
wait until we

00:28:30.600 --> 00:28:33.710
start seeing this stuff. 'Okay, here's

00:28:33.720 --> 00:28:35.389
another one. I asked if they

00:28:35.399 --> 00:28:37.549
remembered any specific miracles where

00:28:37.559 --> 00:28:39.750
God used Brother Seymour, and Sister

00:28:39.760 --> 00:28:41.669
Langford's eyes lit up. "I recall

00:28:41.679 --> 00:28:43.669
witnessing two of the greatest miracles

00:28:43.679 --> 00:28:46.269
where Seymour was powerfully used by

00:28:46.269 --> 00:28:46.279
God."I

00:28:46.279 --> 00:28:48.509
was all ears. First, she told me about

00:28:48.519 --> 00:28:50.669
the man with the wooden leg. Seymour had

00:28:50.679 --> 00:28:52.230
approached a man with a wooden leg and

00:28:52.240 --> 00:28:54.509
asked, "What did you come here for?"The man

00:28:54.519 --> 00:28:56.789
replied, "I want you to pray for my leg;

00:28:56.799 --> 00:28:58.630
it's starting to get

00:28:58.630 --> 00:28:58.640
gangrene

00:28:58.640 --> 00:29:01.110
where the wooden leg

00:29:01.110 --> 00:29:01.120
attaches."Seymour

00:29:01.120 --> 00:29:02.950
replied, "I'm just upset because you have

00:29:02.960 --> 00:29:04.710
the wooden leg on. It would be a

00:29:04.720 --> 00:29:06.350
challenge for God to grow a leg out with

00:29:06.360 --> 00:29:08.149
a wooden leg still

00:29:08.149 --> 00:29:08.159
attached."The

00:29:08.159 --> 00:29:10.389
man removed the wooden leg

00:29:10.399 --> 00:29:12.190
and stood before Seymour, balancing on

00:29:12.200 --> 00:29:14.669
his one good leg. Seymour laid hands on

00:29:14.679 --> 00:29:16.430
the man and proclaimed, "Let Thy name be

00:29:16.440 --> 00:29:18.870
glorified. In the name of Jesus, I command

00:29:18.880 --> 00:29:20.950
this leg to grow out. The gangrene is

00:29:20.960 --> 00:29:23.230
gone; you are healed."Seymour didn't

00:29:23.240 --> 00:29:25.070
preach that night. The miracle spoke for

00:29:25.080 --> 00:29:28.350
itself. Rejoicing was continuous; the

00:29:28.360 --> 00:29:31.149
crowd went wild. The man ran up the

00:29:31.159 --> 00:29:33.190
platform and around the room on two good

00:29:33.200 --> 00:29:35.350
legs. No one could get him to stop

00:29:35.360 --> 00:29:38.710
rejoicing and praising

00:29:38.720 --> 00:29:42.549
God. Praise God! Next, Sister

00:29:42.549 --> 00:29:42.559
Langford

00:29:42.559 --> 00:29:45.470
told of the man with no arm. He had

00:29:45.480 --> 00:29:47.350
lost his arm ten years earlier through a

00:29:47.360 --> 00:29:49.470
work-related accident. The arm had been

00:29:49.480 --> 00:29:51.509
totally severed at the shoulder. Brother

00:29:51.519 --> 00:29:53.350
Seymour asked the crowd, "Would you like

00:29:53.360 --> 00:29:55.149
to see God have a wonderful time here

00:29:55.149 --> 00:29:55.159
tonight?"Some

00:29:55.159 --> 00:29:57.269
of you may remember that

00:29:57.269 --> 00:29:57.279
man's

00:29:57.279 --> 00:29:59.590
leg that grew out about

00:29:59.600 --> 00:30:01.710
a year ago. Seymour then asked the

00:30:01.710 --> 00:30:01.720
one-armed

00:30:01.720 --> 00:30:03.430
man, "Can you work with just the one

00:30:03.430 --> 00:30:03.440
arm?"The

00:30:03.440 --> 00:30:06.070
man answered, "I'm just given the

00:30:06.080 --> 00:30:07.909
minimal paying jobs and I can barely

00:30:07.919 --> 00:30:11.110
make enough money to even

00:30:11.110 --> 00:30:11.120
eat."Seymour

00:30:11.120 --> 00:30:12.630
shook his head and responded,

00:30:12.640 --> 00:30:14.310
"That's not good. Are you married?""Yes.""Got

00:30:14.310 --> 00:30:14.320
kids?""Yes."Seymour

00:30:14.320 --> 00:30:16.630
declared, "This man needs to

00:30:16.640 --> 00:30:18.750
be able to make a living. This man needs

00:30:18.760 --> 00:30:20.350
to work, and he needs to be able to pay

00:30:20.360 --> 00:30:22.310
his tithe. Will you tithe if I pray for

00:30:22.320 --> 00:30:23.909
you and God gives you your arm

00:30:23.909 --> 00:30:23.919
back?"Seymour

00:30:23.919 --> 00:30:26.070
asked teasingly. "Yes,"the man

00:30:26.080 --> 00:30:27.630
replied. Seymour burst out laughing. "I'm

00:30:27.640 --> 00:30:29.509
just having fun."Then he slapped his

00:30:29.519 --> 00:30:30.789
hands on the shoulder itself and

00:30:30.799 --> 00:30:33.070
commanded the arm to grow out. Almost

00:30:33.080 --> 00:30:36.350
instantly, it grew out. The healed man

00:30:36.360 --> 00:30:39.110
stood in total shock, then started moving

00:30:39.120 --> 00:30:41.149
his new arm and inspecting it with his

00:30:41.159 --> 00:30:43.710
other hand, wonder-struck by the miracle. A

00:30:43.720 --> 00:30:45.350
few weeks later, the man came back,

00:30:45.360 --> 00:30:47.549
bringing about two

00:30:47.549 --> 00:30:47.559
hundred

00:30:47.559 --> 00:30:49.669
people with him, telling many at the

00:30:49.679 --> 00:30:51.389
meeting that he had gotten his old job

00:30:51.399 --> 00:30:53.509
back. Many of those that he brought with

00:30:53.519 --> 00:30:55.389
him needed healing and left that evening

00:30:55.399 --> 00:30:57.190
fully restored as people in the crowd

00:30:57.200 --> 00:30:59.710
prayed and laid hands on each of

00:30:59.710 --> 00:30:59.720
them.'Okay,

00:30:59.720 --> 00:31:02.549
pause. Do you not see that? So

00:31:02.559 --> 00:31:04.830
he brought 200 people back, his arm

00:31:04.840 --> 00:31:07.070
grew out—everybody saw and knew who this

00:31:07.080 --> 00:31:10.990
was, this man whose arm was gone—and 200

00:31:11.000 --> 00:31:13.029
people came to

00:31:13.039 --> 00:31:15.509
give their hearts to Jesus Christ. It's

00:31:15.519 --> 00:31:18.509
the goodness of God that brings men into

00:31:18.519 --> 00:31:20.590
repentance. Look at what's going to

00:31:20.600 --> 00:31:22.669
happen. There will be a great shaking to

00:31:22.679 --> 00:31:25.629
awaken, but in this, there will be a great

00:31:25.639 --> 00:31:28.710
harvest of souls. I'm telling you, when we

00:31:28.720 --> 00:31:30.950
start seeing things like this, we

00:31:30.960 --> 00:31:32.710
won't be able to keep the people

00:31:32.720 --> 00:31:34.909
away from church because they're

00:31:34.919 --> 00:31:36.990
going to be so hungry. People are broken

00:31:37.000 --> 00:31:39.110
out there; they're wanting a touch from

00:31:39.120 --> 00:31:42.190
Jesus. And when we start operating

00:31:42.190 --> 00:31:42.200
and

00:31:42.200 --> 00:31:45.590
walking in these demonstrations and

00:31:45.600 --> 00:31:48.870
manifestations of His glory, the people

00:31:48.880 --> 00:31:51.149
are going to come in by the

00:31:51.159 --> 00:31:54.629
groves. You have one more? 'Yeah,

00:32:00.679 --> 00:32:02.950
this

00:32:02.960 --> 00:32:04.350
following miracle took healing

00:32:04.360 --> 00:32:05.590
out to a brand new level for me. I

00:32:05.600 --> 00:32:07.830
guarantee you ask anybody today and

00:32:07.840 --> 00:32:11.750
they'd all agree that Down syndrome...

00:32:22.080 --> 00:32:23.789
can't be healed. Most people would say

00:32:23.799 --> 00:32:25.870
that, but Sister Dundy would tell you

00:32:25.880 --> 00:32:28.110
differently if she were here. She prayed

00:32:28.120 --> 00:32:30.710
for maybe two dozen of those who were

00:32:30.720 --> 00:32:32.549
healed from this disorder, and I was

00:32:32.559 --> 00:32:34.990
lucky enough to meet one of them. I don't

00:32:35.000 --> 00:32:37.029
remember his name, but he was a little

00:32:37.039 --> 00:32:39.509
old man by the time I met him. His face

00:32:39.519 --> 00:32:41.310
had all the characteristics of someone

00:32:41.320 --> 00:32:43.590
who has Down syndrome, but he acted

00:32:43.600 --> 00:32:45.950
completely normal after God touched him

00:32:45.960 --> 00:32:47.669
through the prayers of Sister Dundy. He

00:32:47.679 --> 00:32:49.669
grew up and became a professor of music

00:32:49.679 --> 00:32:52.149
and taught in a California university.

00:32:52.159 --> 00:32:53.830
Sister Dundy remembered the day he was

00:32:53.840 --> 00:32:55.629
healed. He looked at her and said, "You're

00:32:55.639 --> 00:32:57.990
not Jesus."She smiled and the

00:32:58.000 --> 00:32:59.509
mother explained to him that he's fine

00:32:59.519 --> 00:33:01.269
now. Of course, the mother couldn't talk;

00:33:01.279 --> 00:33:02.909
she was shaking her head in disbelief

00:33:02.919 --> 00:33:05.070
and crying—her son was just healed of

00:33:05.080 --> 00:33:07.750
Down syndrome. The next story surprised

00:33:07.760 --> 00:33:09.789
me even more. I still marvel when I think

00:33:09.799 --> 00:33:11.830
of it. One day, Sister Dundy found a

00:33:11.840 --> 00:33:13.710
horribly disfigured child around five years

00:33:13.720 --> 00:33:15.950
old amongst all the people at

00:33:15.950 --> 00:33:15.960
Azusa

00:33:15.960 --> 00:33:18.750
Street. He had scars all around his head.

00:33:18.760 --> 00:33:21.430
His family said that doctors literally

00:33:21.440 --> 00:33:23.549
had to piece his face back together

00:33:23.559 --> 00:33:26.110
after he fell from a staircase onto a

00:33:26.120 --> 00:33:27.950
concrete floor when he was about two

00:33:27.950 --> 00:33:27.960
and a

00:33:27.960 --> 00:33:30.389
half years old. The side of his face that

00:33:30.399 --> 00:33:32.389
took the impact was about one-quarter of an

00:33:32.399 --> 00:33:34.269
inch lower than the rest of his head.

00:33:34.279 --> 00:33:37.710
Sister Dundy could tell he wasn't

00:33:37.720 --> 00:33:40.230
normal mentally either. Her reaction: "Oh,

00:33:40.240 --> 00:33:42.389
how marvelous. God gets glory when things

00:33:42.399 --> 00:33:44.950
like this happen."The father asked, "Things

00:33:44.960 --> 00:33:46.470
like what?""He's going to be

00:33:46.470 --> 00:33:46.480
healed,"she

00:33:46.480 --> 00:33:48.350
declared. See, by this time they didn't

00:33:48.360 --> 00:33:50.990
say, "God will,"they said, "He is

00:33:50.990 --> 00:33:51.000
healed."They

